{
  "stem": "23742.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's one of those reasons why we just couldn't communicate with them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Because of the conditions and the privations that they had suffered, it was difficult to be accurate.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it could have been anything from 16 to 30 or 40.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were all women-- could have been related, but I was-- I couldn't be sure of that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Five to six hours.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were civilians waiting there in the square outside the [INAUDIBLE] station.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were military personnel there, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The members of the medical corps were there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were also some people wearing the Red Cross arm band, which made me to understand that arrangements had-- had been-- had been made.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was six trucks and approximately 20 to each truck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But once they had been dispersed, I lost contact with them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can only assume that once a member of the civilians who were there who had taken one of the prisoners under their care-- there could-- I would most probably assume there was some kind of registration to keep track of them.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I had the papers of the women on my truck, which I handed over to an official.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I assume that the other truck drivers had the same.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I reported back to my unit, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Cleaned up, reported back for duty.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we discussed with our colleagues what we had seen and where we had been.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no restriction.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A lot of our people were keen to hear what had happened and where we had been.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And no, there was no restriction on talking about it, absolutely not, no, no.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remained with my unit for the rest of 1945.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
